aseous pattern appears to be linked to\nresonances in stellar orbits. Among these, the 4:1 resonance plays an important\nrole, as it also determines the extent over which the imposed spiral pattern is\ndynamically self-consistent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Feb 2004 22:51:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Mar 2004 18:22:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
